            <li><strong>Normal wear and tear</strong> from guest use</li>
            <li><strong>Cash, securities, or collectibles</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Shared or common areas</strong> (hallways, lobbies, parking lots)</li>
            <li><strong>Items not disclosed in your listing</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Damage from natural disasters</strong> or pre-existing conditions</li>
            <li><strong>Vehicles, boats, or watercraft</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Identity theft or cyber incidents</strong></li>
          </ul>

